274
00:14:23.697 --> 00:14:25.824
Victim is a. uh. 33...

275
00:14:26.825 --> 00:14:30.369
...year-old white... male.

276
00:14:30.370 --> 00:14:32.288
[button clicks]

277
00:14:32.289 --> 00:14:34.957
- [indistinct radio chatter]
- [indistinct chatter]

278
