and for what?

362
00:18:36.741 --> 00:18:39.117
Your shit job and your shit life?

363
00:18:39.118 --> 00:18:40.702
Come on.

364
00:18:40.703 --> 00:18:44.414
For God's sake. Kay.
go take some credit for something.

365
00:18:44.415 --> 00:18:46.501
