468
00:22:52.789 --> 00:22:55.165
I don't like getting them.
I don't like giving them.

469
00:22:55.166 --> 00:22:56.958
But somebody--

470
00:22:56.959 --> 00:22:59.544
somebody needs to make a choice.

471
00:22:59.545 --> 00:23:00.754
