472
00:23:00.755 --> 00:23:02.923
Yes. motherfucker. you!

473
00:23:02.924 --> 00:23:04.674
You have to choose.

474
00:23:04.675 --> 00:23:07.428
It's either me or her.

475
00:23:21.651 --> 00:23:23.653
[suspenseful music playing]

476
00:23:37.625 --> 00:23:39.210
